Why run like that?
It's not good for you.


557
00:39:02.830 --> 00:39:04.310
Are you listening?

558
00:39:04.910 --> 00:39:07.070
Makes you die sooner.

559
00:39:07.230 --> 00:39:09.470
Then what to say to the boy?

560
